CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Empresa Distribuidora y Comercializadora Norte SA is the largest electricity distribution company in Argentina by the number of customers and volume. The firm's concession area covers the northern portion of the city of Buenos Aires mainly to residential, commercial, industrial, and public service.
